                    <span>I was looking for a book on JPEG files so I could write a program to compress jpeg files for internet use. After reading this book I did come away with some insight on how JPEG compresssion works, however, the code examples in the book only work with JFIF JPEG files. The book says that JFIF format is the most commonly used, but I was unable to compress many of the pictures on my computer...</span>
                  
